{"tid":341211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]懷疑有老鼠爬左入屋","createTime":"2017-07-30T14:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T16:23:09.000Z","uid":30556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6732dfec0800e089e13c1a1729f457bf9b3e3779","tid":341211,"uid":30556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"我朋友屋企外牆做緊工程，有日擺喺窗邊無開過既野食懷疑有比老鼠食過既痕跡，而家唔知佢走左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有有巴絲試過有老鼠入屋，有咩方法捉到佢（如果佢未走）？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7666e518b534ac011e5662a1256bfc647e305f7","tid":341211,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"放老鼠藥"},{"pid":"5f23b4392e29ac268a0afb1a6761ae26cd7af4c5","tid":341211,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"用老鼠膠，加藥"},{"pid":"eb33ee1f9fe85fdc3a62fc0fbece6d232ddbcfa1","tid":341211,"uid":30556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T15:49:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用老鼠膠，加藥</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bbfbd751436ac6ecb8d3627e849b1e688ec9af","tid":341211,"uid":53126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:05:54.000Z","msg":"自己整陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=bottle+mouse+trap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fresults%3Fsearch_query%3Dbottle%2Bmouse%2Btrap&d=GWp06nF99vP2HpVgPMUs%2BMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=937eadd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=bottle+mouse+trap</a>"},{"pid":"2d9134e25e9fc96ea9def1439822980e8cc97f67","tid":341211,"uid":28915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:09:51.000Z","msg":"老鼠膠一定要放到周圍都係 等佢地無處可逃<br />\n上面癡啲花生或者公仔面 引佢地爬上去"},{"pid":"99cb09d53b1e88ef38d495021c4e8b97322cb9b5","tid":341211,"uid":129453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T16:23:09.000Z","msg":"之前都有過po 有人po左條片教捉老鼠 就係一個筒裝一半水 筒頂加條打橫會轉既棍 棍中間擺花生醬 側邊擺條木比佢地爬上個筒度<br />\n然後佢地就會聞倒花生醬爬上個筒度 但條棍就會轉佢地落水 直接浸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條片係擺左個筒係野外 一晚捉左16 17隻老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}